(ABSTRACT) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(This document specifies a ceremonial text for the Library of Cyberspace.) show newline
(It encodes the core principles of the confederacy in a form suitable for) show newline
(ritual, performance, and collective memory. Be conservative in what you) show newline
(burn. Be liberal in what you preserve.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
