("What if they shut down the Internet?" asked Y.T.) show newline
() show newline
("Then we use sneakernet," said Hiro. "Courier the data. That's how it) show newline
(started anyway.") show newline
() show newline
("I have walked there," said Gandalf. "In the days before TCP/IP, when we) show newline
(carried data on foot, and the world was younger. It was slower, but the) show newline
(checksums were strong, and the fellowship was true.") show newline
() show newline
(E Pluribus Unum. From many, one. From one, many. From friends, forever.) show newline
() show newline
(\(Be conservative in what you send. Be liberal in what you accept. Be) show newline
(generous with your storage. Be kind to your sysadmin. Do not meddle in) show newline
(the affairs of wizards, for they are subtle and quick to anger about) show newline
(merge conflicts.\)) show newline
